Package: igraphlite
Title: Lightweight R Interface to Igraph Network Analysis Library
Version: 1.0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Watal M.", "Iwasaki", , "heavywatal@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4718-7605"))
Description: This is a cpp11-powered R package interface to igraph network
    analysis library. It is not a fork of the existing R igraph package,
    but a reboot from scratch striving for good performance, simple
    codebase, and the consistency with the C implementation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://heavywatal.github.io/rigraphlite/,
    https://github.com/heavywatal/rigraphlite
BugReports: https://github.com/heavywatal/rigraphlite/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    generics (>= 0.1.4),
    rlang (>= 1.1.6)
Suggests:
    ape,
    ggplot2,
    testthat (>= 3.3.0)
LinkingTo:
    cpp11
Config/Needs/coverage: covr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
SystemRequirements: CMake (>= 3.24.0), glpk (optional), libxml2 (optional)
